  <brief_title>A Trial Comparing Yield of Confocal Endomicroscopy Guided Biopsies</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Trial Comparing Yield of Confocal Endomicroscopy Guided Biopsies With Random Biopsies in the Detection of Specialized Columnar Epithelium in Barrett's Esophagus</official_title>
  <sponsors>
