  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We wish to determine whether biopsies obtained with the technique of fluorescence-aided
      confocal endomicroscopy will detect more patients with specialized columnar epithelium than
      random biopsies among patients with Barrett's esophagus who are being monitored with
      endoscopy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
